text:
We can't term every promise as a 'FREEBIE'. It's the DUTY of any govt to provide BASIC HUMAN NEEDS to it's citizens.
For ex: Giving food, education, healthcare, limited water/electricity can't be termed as 'FREEBIES' 
At the sametime giving laptops, cycles, ornaments, TVs, mobiles are definitely 'FREEBIES'
The idea is that every citizen has a right to live with bare minimum support from govt in a welfare state. And it's very much possible if the entire corrupt political system is removed with honest political will.
